quran[25{c,v,t}:
82,1,jab aasman phatt jaye ga
82,2,aur jab tarre bikhar jayen ge
82,3,aur jab samandar phaar diye jayen ge
82,4,aur jab qabrain khol di jayen gi
82,5,uss waqt har shakhs ko uss ka agla pichla sab kya dhara maloom ho jaye ga
82,6,"ae ensaan, kis cheez ne tujhe apne uss Rab kareem ki taraf se dhokay mein daal diya"
82,7,"jis ne tujhe peda kya, tujhe nuk suck se durust kya, tujhe mutanasib banaya"
82,8,aur jis soorat mein chaha tujh ko joor kar tayyar kya ?
82,9,"hargiz nahi, balkay ( asal baat yeh hai ke ) tum log jaza o saza ko jutlatay ho"
82,10,halaank tum par nigaran muqarrar hain
82,11,aisay Muaziz katib
82,12,jo tumahray har feal ko jantay hain
82,13,yaqeenan naik log mazay mein hon ge
82,14,aur be shak badkaar log jahannum mein jayen ge
82,15,jaza ke din woh is mein daakhil hon ge
82,16,aur uss se hargiz gayab nah ho saken ge
82,17,aur tum kya jantay ho ke woh jaza ka din kya hai ?
82,18,"haan, tumhe kya khabar ke woh jaza ka din kya hai ?"
82,19,"yeh woh din hai jab kisi shakhs ke liye kuch karna kisi ke bas mein nah hoga, faisla uss din bilkul Allah ke ikhtiyar mein hoga"
83,1,tabahi hai dandi maarny walon ke liye
83,2,jin ka haal yeh hai ke jab logon se letay hain to poora poora letay hain
83,3,aur jab un ko naap kar ya toal kar dete hain to inhen ghata dete hain
83,4,"kya yeh log nahi samajte ke aik barray din ,"
83,5,yeh utha kar laaye jaane walay hain ?
83,6,uss din jabkay sab log Rab alaalmin ke samnay kharray hon ge
